WEBVTT

00:00.847 --> 00:03.676
Oh! Mr. Bond, I was thinking.

00:04.176 --> 00:06.111
Why don't you collect me at my apartment?

00:07.244 --> 00:09.084
It's lovely up here in the mountains.

00:09.897 --> 00:11.068
Nice and cool.

00:12.467 --> 00:16.915
All right. You leave the Port Royal Road out of Kingston.

00:17.343 --> 00:21.365
Then along the Wentworth Road, until you get to the cement factory.

00:22.207 --> 00:23.239
Then you turn left.

00:24.254 --> 00:27.553
Follow the road up the hill, down the other side...

00:28.096 --> 00:30.935
... and two miles further on, on the left...

00:31.328 --> 00:34.277
... Magenta Drive, 2391.

00:36.371 --> 00:37.668
I'll be waiting for you.

